# H180 typology/re-glue/learner builders — DERIVED from the local-only store
# (pwg_ru_translated.jsonl) by build_relationships.py / build_learner_scores.py /
# build_reglue.py / synth_de_first.py. Regenerable, not deliverables, and useless
# without the (gitignored) store — so the bulk machine forms stay local. The
# COMMITTED deliverables are: the builders, the spec docs, the small summary
# tables (relationships_rollup.tsv, edition_deltas.tsv, reglue/PILOT_SUMMARY.tsv,
# reglue/synth_inputs/MANIFEST.tsv + *.prompts.json), and the rendered pilot
# cards reglue/*.md (the human-reviewable output).
src/pwg_ru_relationships.jsonl
pwg_ru/learner_scores.tsv
pwg_ru/reglue/*.json
pwg_ru/reglue/synth_inputs/*.de.txt

# H180 human review sheets (build_h180_review_sheets.py) — the generated HTML
# voting sheets embed translated `ru` bodies from the local-only/unpublished store,
# and THIS REPO IS PUBLIC, so the sheets stay local (open from file://, vote, then
# feed decisions.json to /decisions-apply). Only the generator + the metadata-only
# *_sample.jsonl audit trails (no translations) are committed.
review/h180_*_sheet.html

# H180 Arm-B synthesize-first outputs (synth_de_first.py + Opus-4.8 synth agents):
# the merged German entries embed `de` from the unpublished store (repo public) — local
# only. The numeric scores table (no text) IS committed.
pwg_ru/reglue/synth_outputs/*
!pwg_ru/reglue/synth_outputs/ARMB_SCORES.tsv
